<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0038a01"/><p id="pI01p0038a0101">
<lb ed="C I" n="0038a02"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0038a03"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0038a04"/>但越主梁洪相
<lb ed="C I" n="0038a05"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0038a06"/>　　梁歸喜
<lb ed="C I" n="0038a07"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0038a08"/></p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0038b01"/><p id="pI01p0038b0101">　　　　　　　　大代延昌四年歲次乙未四月一日
<lb ed="C I" n="0038b02"/>比丘郭□勝　造石像一區。為忘弟子　曇豐。
<lb ed="C I" n="0038b03"/>夫大覺淟□□積善。<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>以成其功。四到輪迴。何能超其累。
<lb ed="C I" n="0038b04"/>是以□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">晉</unclear>脩諸利。功益當時。自靈波沖寂。神光遷<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">苑</unclear>。<note n="0038001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30418;＝雖【史】</note><app n="0038001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30418;</rdg></app>復
<lb ed="C I" n="0038b05"/>漸影園□。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">光</unclear>潛□□。自非識體玄宗。栖心妙竟。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">沖</unclear>慮建于靈祇。
<lb ed="C I" n="0038b06"/>像法<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">開</unclear>□□。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">願</unclear>使忘者神生天堂。縱志八定。彌勒一其。值生不退。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">現</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0038b07"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">世</unclear>伏災。四大休□。功□寵祿。子孫樊熾。門族雍和。非□永絕三途曠火輪催軸
<lb ed="C I" n="0038b08"/>　　　　　　　　三有四生。悟<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>生忍。庶□&CB00458;　　<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">散</unclear>。<note n="0038002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30419;＝冀【史】</note><app n="0038002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冀</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30419;</rdg></app>隆剋就。</p>
</div2>
